-- RTL, ProSieben Deal on Internet TV Faces In-Depth German Antitrust Review
-- B y   K a r i n   M a t u s s e k
-- 2010-10-26T12:04:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-26/rtl-prosieben-deal-on-internet-tv-faces-in-depth-german-antitrust-review.html
RTL Group SA and ProSiebenSat.1
Media AG’s plan to set up a joint Internet platform for free
television will be reviewed in depth by German antitrust
regulators. The Bonn-based Federal Cartel Office extended its
probe for three months, the regulator’s spokesman Kay Weidner
said in an interview today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
